<div id="pf51e1" class="pf w46 h359" data-page-no="51e1"><div class="pc pc51e1 w46 h359"><div class="t m68d x34 hbc y2061 ff1 fs30 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What Adventists Believe </div><div class="t m631 x63 h2d y1a8a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During the third and fourth quarters of 1988, Sabbath Schools </div><div class="t m1b9 x4e h2d y1958 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">around the world will turn temporarily from the Bible book cur-</div><div class="t m8b0 x4e h2d y116e ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">riculum we have been studying. In order to revitalize our under-</div><div class="t mb52 x28 h2d y1d96 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">standing of the fundamental beliefs of the Seventh-day Adventist </div><div class="t m25c x28 h2d y195a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church, we will study one of the 27 statements of belief each Sab-</div><div class="t md13 x4e h2d y1dec ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bath over a two-quarter period. </div><div class="t m85e x63 h2d y10d5 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But there is more to this unique approach than reviewing our </div><div class="t m57c x4e h2d yb9a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs. Not only will you become more familiar with the teachings </div><div class="t m387 x28 h2d y18c6 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of your church but you also will be learning how to share your </div><div class="t m67b x4e h2d y639 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs with those who wish to know more about them. </div><div class="t mcff x63 h2d y1566 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Watch for additional information that will give you guidance on </div><div class="t m324 x28 h2d y1997 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how to combine your study of these lessons with supplemental out-</div><div class="t m55c x28 h2d y222b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reach tools such as doctrinal tracts, books, Bible lessons, and mis-</div><div class="t mdc8 x28 h2d y214c ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sionary literature. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
